short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Automatically generate unique test ids for all html elements in a web page for use with automation test tools like Selenium.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Automation Wizard automatically generates unique test ids for all html elements in a web page making the page easily accessible for automation test tools like Selenium.
